title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Mar 24 TH [sebaygo1]
description:
.
							
The Peter Schiff Show
Thursday, 24 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Thursday's guests are:

Rick Santelli, CNBC on-air editor, on the imploding housing market, states moving to adopt gold-backed currencies, and his view of the tea party movement's economic literacy

David Gilmore, founder of Foreign Exchange Analytics, on the merits of a strong dollar


Michael Pento is still guest-hosting. Peter will be back Friday.
